<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>لماذا أنت منحنية</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Why are you stopped down, my soul?
 Why are you groaning?
 Hope in God, he will bring you to life, and you will sing of his power.
 Why has fear worn you out and in it you waste your life?
 Your protector is near you, trust him and you will be secure
 Refrain:
 The living Jesus lives his life of glory in me.
 His resurrection in my example, my life is overflowing in him.
 2-why has worry made you tiresome?
 What can you get out of it?
 Cast all on him, he came make us rich.
 Why has doubt overtaken you, and thoughts go through your mind?
 Our Christ's tomb is empty and his power in us.
 3-why has depression silenced you,
 And you are not getting any closer to your quests?
 He has risen from dead, and is holding our yearnings in his hands.
 Why does death frighten you, and its thorn pains you?
 The grave is not your destinity; it only brings you to glory
 1-لماذا انت منحنيه ويا نفسي تئنين</lyrics>
<hymn_number>6374</hymn_number>
</song>